title: The Peter Schiff Show - 2011 Dec 06 TU [sebaygo1]

The Peter Schiff Show
Tuesday, 06 December 2011


[sebaygo1]


Today's guest is Christian Weller, senior fellow at the Center for American Progress and co-author of Retirement Income: The Crucial Role of Social Security, on why a Consumer Financial Protection Bureau will be just the thing to get Wall St. working again; ALSO, why government should narrow America's income gap.
